 "remarks": "Bright and spacious 3-bedroom, 2.1-bath townhouse ideally located across from Pemberwick Park. The updated eat-in kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a center island, and abundant cabinetry for extra storage. Hardwood floors span the main level, while the spacious primary suite offers vaulted ceilings, an en-suite bath, and generous walk-in closet space. The lower level provides ample storage along with a dedicated home office or flex space. Enjoy central air, a private deck overlooking a level backyard, and a private driveway with parking for up to three vehicles. Just steps from Pemberwick Park&apos;s tennis and basketball courts, baseball fields, playground, and hiking trails. Conveniently located just minutes from The Mill, downtown Glenville&apos;s shops and restaurants, Glenville Elementary School, three daycares, and all major commuter routes.",
